Design Philosophy:
- Clean Architecture with clear separation of concerns
- MVVM pattern for testability
- Offline-first approach for better UX
- Type-safe networking with async/await
- SwiftUI for modern, declarative UI
- Fitness-focused aesthetics (NOT dating app)

Key Decisions:
- SwiftData for persistence (over Core Data)
- Manual DI (simple, no external dependencies)
- URLSession (over Alamofire for simplicity)
- AsyncImage (can upgrade to Kingfisher later)
- NavigationStack (modern iOS 16+ navigation)

Backend Requirements:
- REST API with JWT authentication
- Endpoints: /api/v1/auth/*, /api/v1/users/me, /api/v1/classes/*
- JSON request/response format
- ISO 8601 dates
- HTTPS required

Security:
- JWT tokens in Keychain (not UserDefaults)
- HTTPS only for API calls
- Location permission properly requested
- No sensitive data in logs

